Тест 1:
Входные данные:
user = {
    "login": "SleepyDragon",
    "state": {"location": (10, 20), "inventory": ["apple"], "stats": {"hp": 90}}
}

save_state(user)
restored = load_state("SleepyDragon")
print(restored)

Ожидаемый вывод:
{'location': (10, 20), 'inventory': ['apple'], 'stats': {'hp': 90}}

------------------------------

